arcade.agent.helper

Class ConvertHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.agent.helper.ConvertHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Helper, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable

    public class ConvertHelper
extends java.lang.Object
implements Helper
    Implementation of Helper for converting a cell to a different population.

    ConvertHelper is stepped once. The ConvertHelper will select one cell located at the center of the simulation and convert it to a cell agent of the new population by removing the old cell and creating a new cell with the same age and volume.

    Since:
    2.2
    Version:
    2.3.6
